{"tid":1021522,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"eSm^_^iley 祝巴絲情人節快樂！送親手整嘅朱古力","createTime":"2019-02-14T10:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T14:11:48.000Z","uid":224730,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5edeaba04dad6fb7e73181293f13e50522a31512","tid":1021522,"uid":224730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打情人節快樂，<br />\n譚仔有情人節限定朱古力送，<br />\n我地eSm^_^iley 都有限定朱古力！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夜晚你哋會有咩做呢？<br />\n我地既同事製作左一啲朱古力～<br />\n諗住派比大家，等大家感受下節日氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家各位拍緊拖又或者單身嘅巴絲打都可以開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果想攞朱古力❤：<br />\n7:00pm(大圍地鐵站附近）<br />\n7:30pm(沙田地鐵站附近）<br />\n想拎嘅就快啲嚟搵我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我哋一微米戰隊嘅成員會喺集合點附近等大家嚟<br />\n嚟到嘅巴絲只需要加我地tg: esmileyhk<br />\n話我哋知你喺邊個位<br />\n我哋就會過嚟送上溫馨嘅朱古力<br />\n數量非常有限，送完即止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ozT5aWX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FozT5aWX.jpg&h=c7c9b80a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0912a97d265ced08f8b8109fe2f814b13b1f3fc6","tid":1021522,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"謝謝你"},{"pid":"d01a0a1032dc9671532008779b7951be385a51c2","tid":1021522,"uid":224730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0912a97d265ced08f8b8109fe2f814b13b1f3fc6","tid":1021522,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"謝謝你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Halo"},{"pid":"501e3c0b5ccae2c604854db657be2cb29ebcce5e","tid":1021522,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d01a0a1032dc9671532008779b7951be385a5